{"word":"H2673 - חָצָה - châtsâh - khaw-tsaw' - Divide","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָצָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châtsâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-tsaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Divide"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பங்கிடு, பிரி, வகு, ஆயுளின் நாட்களில் பாதிவரையிரு.பகு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to divide, to cut in two, to cut short, to live half (of one's life)"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to divide"},{"paragraph":"2) to half, to cut in two"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be divided"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root (compare <a href=\"#/H2686 - חָצַץ - châtsats - khaw-tsats'/2686\">H2686</a>); to <i>cut</i> or <i>split</i> in two; to <i>halve: - </i>divide, X live out half, reach to the midst, part."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2673 - חָצָה - châtsâh - khaw-tsaw'/2673\">H2673</a>, <a href=\"#/H2676 - חָצֹות - châtsôwth - khaw-tsoth'/2676\">H2676</a>, <a href=\"#/H2677 - חֵצִי - chêtsîy - khay-tsee'/2677\">H2677</a>, <a href=\"#/H2678 - חִצִּי - chitstsîy - khits-tsee'/2678\">H2678</a>, <a href=\"#/H3183 - יַחְצְאֵל - Yachtsᵉʼêl - yakh-tseh-ale'/3183\">H3183</a>, <a href=\"#/H3184 - יַחְצְאֵלִי - Yachtsᵉʼêlîy - yakh-tseh-ay-lee'/3184\">H3184</a>, <a href=\"#/H3185 - יַחְצִיאֵל - Yachtsîyʼêl - yakh-tsee-ale'/3185\">H3185</a>, <a href=\"#/H4275 - מֶחֱצָה - mechĕtsâh - mekh-ets-aw'/4275\">H4275</a>, <a href=\"#/H4276 - מַחֲצִית - machătsîyth - 